{"type":"message","id":"a3c1b19a","parentId":"abdd6553","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:26:26.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me follow the Session Startup sequence from AGENTS.md:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — already loaded in Project Context\n2. Read `USER.md` — already loaded in Project Context\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION: Read `MEMORY.md` — already loaded in Project Context\n5. Read session context from `~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json`\n6. Read the most recent session summary\n\nLet me check today's date: April 14, 2026 (Tuesday). So I need to read memory/2026-04-14.md and memory/2026-04-13.md, plus the most recent session summary.\n\n\nI should also scan for any existing session summaries to understand what context might already be available.","thinkingSignature":"03b962efe953553582301480726785fbfbeaf066c5502146582f6bcb2fe10167"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_35b7ftrd9o7q_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -t ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/ 2>/dev/null | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_35b7ftrd9o7q_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -t ~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json 2>/dev/null | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":261,"cacheRead":19750,"cacheWrite":145,"totalTokens":20210,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.00031319999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0011849999999999999,"cacheWrite":0.000054375,"total":0.001568775}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776173180794,"responseId":"062d737b194ee2253bdf45b3c441dea4"}}
