{"type":"message","id":"bbded4a6","parentId":"78b0c4ad","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:37:56.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I can do a /new command myself. Let me think - can I trigger a /new session? \n\nIn the OpenClaw framework, /new is typically a user-initiated command that resets the session. As an AI, I don't have a direct tool to trigger /new - that would require me to send a message to myself that looks like \"/new\", which could create a loop, or use some internal API.\n\nLet me think about what I can actually do here. Looking at the tools available, I don't see a direct \"/new\" or \"session reset\" tool. The `sessions_send` tool can send messages to other sessions, but not reset the current one.\n \nWait, I could try sending a /new command through the gateway API to the current session, which might trigger a reset - though I'm not entirely sure if that would create an infinite loop or if the gateway would handle it properly.\n\nAlternatively, I could spawn a sub-agent with a task asking it to perform /new, since the session management might work differently for spawned agents. But the most direct approach would probably be to just ask the user to run /new themselves so I can immediately inspect whether bootstrap was injected.","thinkingSignature":"2745ef56c2ccecebb416a2dd897ff3cc3449ac5c7525658d872612921edde2db"},{"type":"text","text":"<toolthinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n用户问\"你能new？\"— 想知道 AI 自身能否触发 /new 重置会话。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n- 作为 AI，我没有直接调用 /new 的工具命令\n- sessions_send 可以向其他 session 发消息，但不能向当前 session 发系统级 reset 命令\n- 如果我发 \"/new\" 文字给自己，gateway 可能会当作普通消息处理，而非触发 session reset\n- 可以尝试 sessions_spawn 隔离环境，但 /new 是 main session 的 reset 操作\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n/reset 触发需要 gateway 处理特殊命令字，可能不在工具权限范围内。\n最直接的方式还是让用户在当前 UI 触发 /new，我立刻查 bootstrapFiles 是否注入。\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n坦白说我没有直接触发 /new 的能力。给出最实用的替代方案。\n</toolthinking>\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 做不到——/new 是 gateway 的会话管理命令，我没有直接调它的工具权限。\n\n**最实用的验证方式**：你在 UI 里手动发一次 `/new`，我立刻在下一条消息里检查 bootstrapFiles 有没有拿到 session-summary。\n\n或者，如果你能给我一个**其他会话的 session key**，我可以往那个 session 塞一条触发消息，看 bootstrap 是否工作。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":517,"cacheRead":19750,"cacheWrite":21808,"totalTokens":42129,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0006204,"cacheRead":0.0011849999999999999,"cacheWrite":0.008178,"total":0.009999599999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776173856057,"responseId":"062d76206d3512100352ec18b3701ea4"}}
